          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1631617641805-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-8 min or until golden, stirring frequently</p><p>Once golden, transfer the <strong>golden breadcrumbs</strong> to a bowl until ready to serve and reserve the pan for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1631617646510-x200.jpg",
