            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>cooked potatoes</strong> to a low heat with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>double cream</strong> (save the rest for later!), 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> [100ml]<strong> </span>milk </strong>and<strong> </strong>a few knobs of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mash until smooth – this is your <strong>pomme purée</strong></p><p>Tip: For extra smooth pomme purée add to a food processor and blitz until very smooth</p><p>Set the pomme purée aside (keep it in the pot!), ready to reheat later</p>",
