      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat and pat your<strong> rump steak[s]</strong> dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper, then drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and season with<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>steak</strong> to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium- rare, cook for 3-4 min on each side; for medium, cook for 4-5 min on each side</p><p>Once the steak is cooked, transfer to a clean plate to rest (reserve the pan)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
