      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>rump steak </strong>and<strong> peppercorn sauce</strong> with the <strong>shredded kale </strong>and <strong>pomme purée</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>golden breadcrumbs</strong> over the pomme purée and drizzle with your<strong> truffle oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
